Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.20,0:01:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,HYUNCKEL, THE DARK SWORDSMAN
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.25,0:01:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not over!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.19,0:01:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That stance...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.23,0:01:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Avan Strash!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.43,0:02:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You call this Avan Strash?\NDon't make me laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.87,0:02:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That was just a cheap imitation!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.86,0:02:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You know the lesson, "Slice the earth,\Nslice the sea, slice the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.03,0:02:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And what slices everything\Nis Avan Strash."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.66,0:02:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Fighting you, I could tell you haven't\Nmastered the Avan Style Sword Technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.41,0:02:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words,\Nthe third skill, Air Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.77,0:02:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Air Slash?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.25,0:02:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.56,0:02:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.76,0:02:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you complete\Nthe Special Hard Course,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.03,0:02:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll probably learn Air Slash\Non the seventh day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.82,0:02:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The last?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.61,0:02:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It's that difficult\Nof a skill to learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.35,0:02:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I only trained\Nwith Master Avan for three days.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.75,0:02:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I can't use Air Slash.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.25,0:02:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the greatest\NAvan Style Sword Technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.51,0:03:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,When Earth, Wave, and Air are mastered,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.05,0:03:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Avan Strash shows its true ultimate power!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.68,0:03:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Basically, your attack now\Nis merely an incomplete imitation!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.43,0:03:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I can use an imitation like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.09,0:03:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Avan Strash!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.84,0:03:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.14,0:03:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So you two are up next?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.04,0:03:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't let you use\NMaster Avan's skills for evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.29,0:03:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Three against one...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.15,0:03:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll have to use my secret weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.82,0:03:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,As a warrior, I can't use spells.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.55,0:03:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So Vearn, the Dark King,\Ngave me the ultimate armour.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.56,0:03:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,A supreme armour that can repel\Nany and all attack spells!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.10,0:03:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,When I don it, I become unbeatable!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.27,0:04:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,A supreme armour?\NI don't see any armour anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.07,0:04:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Look closely. It's right in front of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.68,0:04:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Amudo!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.99,0:04:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,His sword is his armour?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.63,0:04:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. This Dark Armour Blade\Nis both the ultimate weapon
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.39,0:04:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and the ultimate armour!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.96,0:04:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,H-He's bluffing! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.29,0:04:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Merami!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not working!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.11,0:04:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,How about this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.81,0:04:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Gira!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.06,0:04:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.28,0:05:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.11,0:05:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! I just learned that spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.95,0:05:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Now do you see why I'm unbeatable?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.93,0:05:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This armour is impervious\Nto all attack spells.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.23,0:05:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And no one in the world\Ncan best me at sword fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.97,0:05:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't. I won't fight a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.95,0:05:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate me!\NEven women can risk their lives in battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.95,0:05:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Even more so, if it's for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.28,0:05:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,A likely lesson from Avan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.12,0:05:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You learned it too, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.61,0:05:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Avan would never grant\Nan Insignia of Avan to someone unworthy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.61,0:05:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that deep down...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.95,0:05:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.24,0:05:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.93,0:06:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I only carried it around\Nto find Avan or his students...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.46,0:06:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,so I could kill them myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.01,0:06:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?! Why do you hate him so much?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.24,0:06:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Because Avan is my father's killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.74,0:06:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,His killer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.18,0:06:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This continent of Holkia\Nwas once the Dark Lord Hadlar's base.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.61,0:06:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The old Dark Army razed towns\Nand was the cause of many casualties.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.08,0:06:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.39,0:06:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That child was me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.71,0:06:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was raised in Hadlar's Underground\NPalace by the Hell Knight Bartos.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.63,0:06:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The only reason he was allowed to\Nraise a human child was because{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.53,0:06:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bartos was the strongest knight\Nin the Dark Army.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.78,0:06:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And he was the guardian of the Hell Gate\Nwhich led to Hadlar's chambers.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.98,0:07:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall name you Hyunckel
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.60,0:07:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,after a legendary swordsman\Nwho once ruled the Underworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.40,0:07:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I couldn't leave the Palace,\Nbut I grew up without questioning it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.10,0:07:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.43,0:07:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.21,0:07:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As my father, Bartos was\Nthe first man to teach me warmth.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.89,0:07:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's just like me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.76,0:07:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But one day...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.85,0:07:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Bartos! The Hero is attacking!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.73,0:07:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He's finally come!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.27,0:07:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel, as guardian of the Dark Lord,\NI must fight the Heroes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.19,0:07:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's possible I may die.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.57,0:07:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You mustn't leave this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.85,0:08:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I die,\NI hope you'll grow up strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.71,0:08:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.17,0:08:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.26,0:08:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With the Dark Lord's death cry,\Nall fell silent.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.52,0:08:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.44,0:08:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.57,0:08:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.53,0:08:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Undead, unlike other monsters,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.06,0:08:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}cannot maintain themselves\Nwithout the Dark Lord's power.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With Hadlar's death,\Nand the loss of his Dark Power,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.52,0:08:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}my father...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.75,0:08:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hyunckel...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.80,0:08:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.14,0:09:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel... thank you for the memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.52,0:09:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He crumbled to ashes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.23,0:09:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.57,0:09:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's ironic.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.45,0:09:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The man who happened to find me was Avan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.47,0:09:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You are...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.08,0:09:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.44,0:09:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He had no way of knowing who I was.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.11,0:09:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He must have assumed I was a boy\Nkidnapped by monsters.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.63,0:09:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I knew immediately that\Nhe was the Hero, and my father's killer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.39,0:09:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,At that moment, I swore\Nthat I'd gain strength and kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.19,0:09:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I became Avan's student\Nand learned to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.50,0:09:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So that I could kill him\Nwith what he taught me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.84,0:10:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.12,0:10:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I know how you feel, but Master Avan...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.22,0:10:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,"Was just fighting for justice"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.17,0:10:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Justice or not, it doesn't change\Nthe fact that he took my father's life!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.26,0:10:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,My father died as ashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.86,0:10:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If that is justice...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.34,0:10:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,then justice itself is my enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.18,0:10:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Now to finish you off...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.95,0:10:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,My own special attack\Nthat I intended to use on Avan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.02,0:10:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,A sword from his helmet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.03,0:10:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.53,0:10:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.70,0:10:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai! Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.16,0:10:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the attack I developed to defeat\Nthe Avan Style Sword Technique...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.92,0:10:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Bloody Sukuraido!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.47,0:11:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel, you've gained the skills\Nof a full-fledged warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.47,0:11:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, I present you with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.31,0:11:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.44,0:11:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Consider it a certificate of graduation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.94,0:11:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're far from\Nbeing a complete warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.42,0:11:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Your blade seems to have\Na strange malice or animosity to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.82,0:11:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.14,0:11:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.30,0:11:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know a man named Bartos?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.66,0:11:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.68,0:11:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Bartos was the strongest knight\Nof the Dark Army...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.69,0:11:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and my father!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.92,0:11:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The malice you sense in my blade is\Nmy hatred towards you, my father's killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.41,0:11:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.35,0:11:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.86,0:11:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.61,0:12:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What have I done?\NI instinctively fought back!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.95,0:12:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if I hadn't,\NI'm sure he would have killed me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.18,0:12:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What talent with a blade!\NIt was like a demon's sword!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.12,0:12:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.46,0:12:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.10,0:12:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Avan...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.68,0:12:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I failed, but I was rescued\Nby the Dark King's trusted servant,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.79,0:12:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mystvearn, the Shadow Vizier,\Nand survived.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.98,0:12:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Since then, I've continued to train\Nas a warrior of the Dark Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.05,0:12:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This attack now far surpasses\Nthe power of Avan Strash!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.99,0:12:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Your ill-advised dodging\Nhas only increased your suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.33,0:12:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me end it for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.96,0:13:03.47,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,MAGIC BULLET GUN
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.97,0:13:08.47,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}IONAZUN{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}\NEXPLOSION-TYPE SPELL
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.18,0:13:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's strong!\NStronger than anyone we've faced before!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.02,0:13:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is he really unbeatable?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.23,0:13:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No. That's impossible!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.37,0:13:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everyone has a weakness,\Nno matter how strong!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.99,0:13:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.47,0:13:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'll never give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.47,0:13:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if that bullet contains\Na Begirama or Ionazun,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.77,0:13:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,you won't be able to scratch my armour.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.31,0:13:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll see. You never know unless you try!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.84,0:13:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this Manusa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.72,0:13:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse your foolish games.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.32,0:14:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If I use my inner eye to sense\Nyour presence, your Manusa is useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.33,0:14:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right there! If I can hit him there,\Nan attack spell should work!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.79,0:14:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all or nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.00,0:14:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Mera!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.47,0:14:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He dodged it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.14,0:14:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.41,0:14:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.47,0:14:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Mera!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.90,0:14:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Wave Slash?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.03,0:14:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You have no power,\Nyet you insist on troubling me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.34,0:14:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.62,0:15:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You have spirit.\NThat much is worth praise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.00,0:15:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is Dai really no match for him?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.25,0:15:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sure he's a great swordsman,\Nbut Dai's beaten Hadlar and Crocodine!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.30,0:15:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know! It's that mark!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.22,0:15:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That mark has always allowed Dai\Nto use extraordinary power!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.02,0:15:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai! Use that power!\NUse the power of that mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.28,0:15:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you babbling about now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.91,0:15:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Dai?!\NGet mad! Get mad and fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.54,0:15:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Why won't you get mad, Dai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.33,0:15:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My father died as ashes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.77,0:15:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If that is justice...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.18,0:15:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}then justice itself is my enemy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.26,0:15:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.93,0:15:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This should keep you from using\Nyour bothersome tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.94,0:16:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.52,0:16:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Tomakugutsosho!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.90,0:16:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This skill uses Dark Aura\Nto bind an opponent!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.41,0:16:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally, it's used to control corpses.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.83,0:16:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.80,0:16:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, you're nothing but my puppet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.43,0:16:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.77,0:16:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.92,0:16:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.06,0:16:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Bloody Sukuraido!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.22,0:16:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.68,0:16:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.26,0:16:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo, Hyunckel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.79,0:16:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Beast King Crocodine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.40,0:16:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodine...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.75,0:16:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You survived?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.25,0:16:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.69,0:16:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly what it looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.61,0:16:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you kill Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.70,0:17:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You there, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.72,0:17:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yessir! What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.10,0:17:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Take Dai and escape with that Garuda!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.81,0:17:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.21,0:17:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still too weak to defeat Hyunckel!\NYou have to escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.82,0:17:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.94,0:17:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Some monsters will only obey\Nmy direct commands.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.32,0:17:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That Garuda is one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.85,0:17:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But Maam...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.77,0:17:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.21,0:17:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel isn't the type\Nto kill a girl, no matter the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.07,0:17:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do something about the girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.34,0:17:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, you must escape with Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.01,0:17:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think I'll just let that happen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.24,0:17:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still one of the Six\NLegion Commanders of the Dark Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.85,0:17:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I can take you down with me if I have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.60,0:17:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.90,0:17:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have the strength right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.51,0:17:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.03,0:17:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Your armour may be\Nbrand new, but I can tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.51,0:18:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Your wounds from your previous battle\Nhaven't fully healed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.31,0:18:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Your steel hide is nothing more\Nthan a cracked shield right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.25,0:18:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.69,0:18:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.82,0:18:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.22,0:18:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even if it kills me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.75,0:18:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Maam's still...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.04,0:18:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.96,0:18:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.59,0:18:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Of the Six Legion Commanders,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.73,0:18:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I believed that at least you\Nand Baran were worth respecting!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.68,0:18:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,How disappointing\Nthat you'd submit to a brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.03,0:18:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I merely couldn't stand seeing someone\Nwho beat me lose to someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.02,0:18:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The argument of the defeated.\NHow the Beast King has fallen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.15,0:19:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If you won't move,\NI'll just have to run you through!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.37,0:19:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.24,0:19:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would someone like you\Ncare so much about them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.02,0:19:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,They're enemies of our Dark Army!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.23,0:19:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,"Our Dark Army..."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.84,0:19:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.84,0:19:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It never seemed like you were\Nfighting for the Dark Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.30,0:19:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You always looked like you were\Nfighting out of hatred for humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.35,0:19:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I was the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.94,0:19:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I looked down on humans.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.98,0:19:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought they were puny,\Npathetic creatures.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.45,0:19:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But fighting Dai and his friends\Nmade me realize...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.72,0:19:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}humans are strong\Nand compassionate creatures!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.70,0:19:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They can work together\Nand can share in joy and sadness!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.13,0:19:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're not like us monsters,\Nwho are alone in our strength!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.19,0:20:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Enough of your nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.88,0:20:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way a human like you\Ncan't realize their greatness!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.35,0:20:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you see\Nthat you're lying to yourself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.93,0:20:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.66,0:20:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tears?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.46,0:20:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel... it's good to be a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.92,0:20:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,When I'm reborn again,\NI hope it's as... a human...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.34,0:20:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodine...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.39,0:20:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Moruge.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.99,0:20:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a problem, Sir Hyunckel?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.85,0:20:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my! Isn't that...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.83,0:20:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Tend to his wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.29,0:21:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, I don't see\Nhow he's going to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.34,0:21:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter. Consider it mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.13,0:21:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And take this woman\Nto the Underground Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.80,0:21:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Who is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.55,0:21:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A hostage. Throw her in a cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.60,0:21:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.00,0:21:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So long as I have her,\Nthey're sure to come rescue her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.70,0:21:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When they do, I'll finish them!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.01,0:21:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're awake, Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.56,0:21:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp! Where are we?! Where's Hyunckel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.73,0:21:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He beat us.\NThe two of us managed to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.54,0:21:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Maam?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.17,0:21:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hopefully, she's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.28,0:21:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Our pursuers found us already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.74,0:21:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Are you hurt?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.16,0:21:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't happen to be Dai, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.14,0:21:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,How does he know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.60,0:21:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.15,0:22:25.90,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}yasashisa wa yasashii hito ga tsukaeru mahou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.15,0:22:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kindness is the magic of kind people{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.07,0:22:32.91,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}jaa boku wa tada no hito de iru shikanaino?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.07,0:22:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then do I have no choice\NBut to just be a normal person?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.08,0:22:36.12,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}doudarou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.08,0:22:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not sure{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.42,0:22:44.09,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kaeru basho wa ne kawatte yuku kedo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.42,0:22:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if the place I call home may change{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.25,0:22:46.63,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}naa kaasan boku wa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.25,0:22:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Listen to me, Mother{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.80,0:22:52.76,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mamoru hito wo kaetari shinai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.80,0:22:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will never change those I protect{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.22,0:22:57.43,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}anata wa nannte iukana{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.22,0:22:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder what you'd say{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.60,0:23:01.65,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tokiyori yowaki de chippoke de{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.60,0:23:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At times I can be cowardly and small{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.81,0:23:08.11,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mayou koto ni mo mayou boku ni nannte iukana{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.81,0:23:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What would you say to me\NAs I hesitate to even hesitate?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.28,0:23:13.95,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}sagashite ita kyou to chigatte{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.28,0:23:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unlike the today that I sought{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.12,0:23:19.25,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ochikonnde shimau boku wo warau no darou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.12,0:23:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure you'd laugh at my disappointment{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.60,0:23:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The difference\Nin their strengths was clear.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.10,0:23:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thanks to Crocodine's sacrifice,\NDai and Popp managed to escape.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.65,0:23:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They begin to form a plan to counter\NHyunckel's overwhelming strength.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.57,0:23:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The battle to rescue Maam from her prison\Nin the Underground Palace begins!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.24,0:23:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,DRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.70,0:23:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"The Collaborative Zapple"{\i0}
